c: 6
v: 165
t: "Wahi hai jisne tumko zameen ka khalifa banaya, aur tum mein se baaz ko baaz ke muqable mein zyada buland darje diya, taa-ke jo kuch tumko diya hai usi mein tumhari aazmaish karey. Behsak tumhara Rubb saza dene mein bhi bahut tez hai aur bahut darguzar karne aur reham farmane wala bhi hai"